latestIgtvVideos.title: My Day to Night Skincare regime ft. @lrwonderindia
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
On a clean face after shower, I apply: 
1. Wonder Snail serum - repairs, soothe & stimulates the skin
2. LR Wonder Star Face Cream- enriched with Plant Placenta, Vitamin E & Hyaluronic Acid : helps in hydration & renders flawless skin
3. LR Wonder Body Cream - formulated with Bee Venom & Caffeine: renders smooth, toned & radiant skin

In the night, once I take off my make up with the @simplynam.beauty makeup removal towel, I apply:

1. Wonder Caviar Mask (once a week): for a natural lifting effect & silky shiny look
2. LR Wonder Caviar Serum - repairs my skin for a silky smooth finish
3. LR Wonder Caviar Face Cream - ultra moisturising 24hr anti-ageing cream

@lrwonderindia #Skincare #Skinvestment
